      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber">832.7001-2</ph> Contract clause.</title>
      <conbody>
         <p xtrc="P">The contracting officer shall insert the clause at <xref outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref "
                  base="Section_852_232_72_T48_50216422143"
                  href="Section_852_232_72_T48_50216422143.dita#Section_852_232_72_T48_50216422143">852.232-72</xref>, Electronic Submission of Payment Requests, in solicitations and contracts exceeding the micro-purchase threshold, except those for which the contracting officer has directed otherwise under <xref outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref "
                  base="Section_832_7001_T48_5021329712"
                  href="Section_832_7001_T48_5021329712.dita#Section_832_7001_T48_5021329712">832.7001</xref>, and those paid with a Governmentwide commercial purchase card.


</p>
